Well, I have had a busy few weeks! 

1. The ILC team Inclusive Leadership Compass (Dr Sandy Caspi Sable & Bernadette Dillon) had an amazing session in San Fransisco with the incredible Michelle Gethers  CDO at Visa and Visa’s Global Top 300 leaders. I was so fortunate to tag along.
 
2. Next my good friend and CDO at the NBA 
Lesley Slaton Brown invite me to two discussions with several of the Inclusion leads at the NBA teams and seperate discussion with some of her counterparts at NFL, MLB, NASCAR and several other professional sports organizations. 

3. Wrapped up in Austin at #ITSMF (Information Technology Senior Management forum S2 Symposium! What an incredible group of Black Technology Leaders. A true pleasure to be back!!!

TianEn Stephenson 
Tia Buckham-White, CPC 
CurVie Burton
